          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F30_moped_ebike_page_48V20Ah.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>48V 20Ah</strong> Removable Battery<br/><br/></p>",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>48V 20Ah high-capacity battery</strong> delivers a massive <strong>70-mile PAS range</strong>, providing the ultimate balance of power and endurance. With its <strong>removable design</strong>, you can easily <strong>charge anywhere</strong> and enjoy the freedom to explore deeper into the wild. Reliable, convenient, and built for <strong>long-distance thrills</strong>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_6M3dHz": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 96,
            "item_margin_bottom": 70,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F30_moped_ebike_page_full_suspension.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong> Full Suspension System</strong><br/>Ride Smooth, Dominate the Wild</p>",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>PostJoy F30</strong> is engineered with a professional-grade full suspension system, transforming the roughest trails into your personal playground. At the front, the <strong>high-travel hydraulic fork</strong> is built to soak up heavy hits and high-speed vibrations, while the <strong>rear monoshock</strong> provides exceptional stability, ensuring your rear wheel stays planted for maximum traction during hill attacks.</p><p>Whether you're sticking a landing from a backyard jump, shredding through muddy mountain tracks, or navigating bumpy urban shortcuts, the GT16’s suspension delivers a <strong>perfectly balanced, stable, and plush ride</strong>. Combined with its agile <strong>99 lbs lightweight frame</strong>, you get a machine that doesn't just ride—it conquers any terrain with total control and comfort.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_VNaYcH": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F30_moped_ebike_page_all_terrain_fat_tires.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>All-Terrain Monster Fat Tires</strong><br/>Maximum Stability. Dominate Every Surface.</p>",
            "content": "<p><br/>Featuring <strong>massive 20x4.0-inch fat tires</strong>, the  provides a massive contact patch for <strong>unmatched stability</strong>. Whether you're gliding over loose sand, thick snow, or rugged forest trails, these high-volume tires deliver <strong>superior floatation and grip</strong>. Conquer the elements with confidence and style.<br/><br/></p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_PPeP6c": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F30_moped_ebike_page_nfc_smart_unlock.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong>Tap to Unlock.</strong> Ready to Ride.</p>",
            "content": "<p>The PostJoy F30 features NFC smart unlock, giving you a faster and more convenient way to activate your e-bike. Simply tap your NFC card near the display area to unlock the bike and get ready to ride in seconds — no complicated steps, no unnecessary delay.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        }
      },
